{"tid":1580431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解港奸咁多, 又唔會受到懲罰","createTime":"2019-09-19T05:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T05:28:26.000Z","uid":260361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e182c214ec2b6370c46a4c41c2af78ea92ec1fc","tid":1580431,"uid":260361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"公司要我上廣州, 坐膠鐵, 成車都係香港人, 一到深圳北條八婆(紅圈)就開始挑釁, 不停話示威者係曱甴, 叫人夠膽就而家叫五大訴求, 夠膽去天安門抗議。另一條人渣(綠圈)加入, 話示威者無性, 搞到東鐵出軌。八婆係咁好大聲叫車上有人唔同意就打佢。我除左影大頭之外乜都唔敢做。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrEvoas.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrEvoas.png&h=3daf18ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ck2s9Qt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fck2s9Qt.png&h=77a28c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2X4GuQv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2X4GuQv.png&h=c6385a2a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}